IF WEIGHT #8 /* Triggers after states #: 59 58 12 63 108 79 82 95 even though they appear after this state */ ~  CreatureInArea("AR0201") Global("Appearance","GLOBAL",1) Global("Gate_Open","GLOBAL",0) Global("Soego","GLOBAL",0)
~ THEN BEGIN 0 // from:
SAY #1431 /* ~You see a tired-looking man in a faded black robe. His narrow face is extremely pale, and he doesn't look as if he has been sleeping: his shoulders are slumped, and the flesh sags loosely beneath his bloodshot eyes. He doesn't appear to notice you... he must mistake you for one of the cadaverous workers.~ */
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1432 /* ~"Greetings."~ */ GOTO 1
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1433 /* ~"Who are you?"~ */ GOTO 1
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1434 /* ~"What is this place?"~ */ GOTO 1
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1435 /* ~"I had some questions..."~ */ GOTO 1
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1436 /* ~Leave him in peace.~ */ EXIT
END

IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 1 // from: 0.0 0.1 0.2 0.3
SAY #1437 /* ~The Dustman's head snaps up as you address him. "Par... pardon? Did you just speak to me?"~ */
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1438 /* ~"Yes, I did. I had some questions..."~ */ JOURNAL #63982 /* ~I met a Dustman named Soego at the Mortuary front gate... he looks tired, as if he hasn't slept in weeks. Judging from the eyes and pallor of his skin, it looks like he has caught some sort of illness. ~ */ GOTO 2
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1439 /* ~"No. No, I didn't."~ */ DO ~IncrementGlobalOnceEx("GLOBALChaotic_Soego_1","GLOBALLaw",-1) JOURNAL #63982 /* ~I met a Dustman named Soego at the Mortuary front gate... he looks tired, as if he hasn't slept in weeks. Judging from the eyes and pallor of his skin, it looks like he has caught some sort of illness. ~ */ GOTO 2
IF ~  CheckStatGT(Protagonist,10,CHR) ~ THEN REPLY #1440 /* ~Become deathly silent.~ */ GOTO 3
IF ~  CheckStatLT(Protagonist,11,CHR) ~ THEN REPLY #1441 /* ~Become deathly silent.~ */ GOTO 4
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1442 /* ~Leave. Quickly.~ */ GOTO 5
END

IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 2 // from: 1.0 1.1 3.0 3.3 4.0 4.1
SAY #1443 /* ~"By the powers!" The Dustman jumps, then stares intently at you. You notice his eyes aren't bloodshot as much as they have a red tinge to them. "Sirrah, you force an unflattering confession from me: you make a convincing zombie." He bows slightly. "I am Soego. May I ask your business here..." He glances at your scars. "...looking like that?" ~ */
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1444 /* ~"It's none of your concern."~ */ GOTO 6
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1445 /* ~"I'm not certain what I'm doing here. I woke up on one of the slabs upstairs, and my memory's... a little foggy."~ */ GOTO 7
IF ~  CheckStatGT(Protagonist,10,CHR) ~ THEN REPLY #1446 /* ~"I got turned around in the halls here, and I can't seem to find the exit. Can you help me?"~ */ GOTO 8
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1447 /* ~"I'm trying to get out of here."~ */ GOTO 13
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1448 /* ~"I needed a change."~ */ DO ~IncrementGlobalOnceEx("GLOBALChaotic_Soego_2","GLOBALLaw",-1) ~ GOTO 16
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #4999 /* ~"I really don't have time for this. Farewell."~ */ GOTO 17
END

IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 3 // from: 1.2
SAY #1449 /* ~The Dustman studies you for a moment, then shakes his head. "More imaginings..." He sighs and rubs his eyes. "These fever spells are getting worse..."~ */
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1450 /* ~"It's not your imagination. I had some questions..."~ */ JOURNAL #63982 /* ~I met a Dustman named Soego at the Mortuary front gate... he looks tired, as if he hasn't slept in weeks. Judging from the eyes and pallor of his skin, it looks like he has caught some sort of illness. ~ */ GOTO 2
IF ~  CheckStatGT(Protagonist,12,DEX) ~ THEN REPLY #1451 /* ~Snap his neck while he is distracted.~ */ GOTO 19
IF ~  CheckStatLT(Protagonist,13,DEX) ~ THEN REPLY #1452 /* ~Snap his neck while he is distracted.~ */ GOTO 22
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1453 /* ~"I had some questions."~ */ JOURNAL #63982 /* ~I met a Dustman named Soego at the Mortuary front gate... he looks tired, as if he hasn't slept in weeks. Judging from the eyes and pallor of his skin, it looks like he has caught some sort of illness. ~ */ GOTO 2
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1454 /* ~Leave quietly.~ */ EXIT
END

IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 4 // from: 1.3
SAY #1455 /* ~The Dustman looks carefully at you, then leans in... his lips peel back, revealing a row of dirty, sharp teeth, and he begins to sniff at you like a rat.~ */
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1456 /* ~"Uh... why in hell's name are you sniffing me?"~ */ DO ~SetGlobal("Soego","Global",1) JOURNAL #63982 /* ~I met a Dustman named Soego at the Mortuary front gate... he looks tired, as if he hasn't slept in weeks. Judging from the eyes and pallor of his skin, it looks like he has caught some sort of illness. ~ */ GOTO 2
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1457 /* ~"Look, I had some questions for you..."~ */ DO ~SetGlobal("Soego","Global",1) JOURNAL #63982 /* ~I met a Dustman named Soego at the Mortuary front gate... he looks tired, as if he hasn't slept in weeks. Judging from the eyes and pallor of his skin, it looks like he has caught some sort of illness. ~ */ GOTO 2
IF ~  CheckStatGT(Protagonist,12,DEX) ~ THEN REPLY #1458 /* ~Snap his neck when he leans in.~ */ GOTO 19
IF ~  CheckStatLT(Protagonist,13,DEX) ~ THEN REPLY #1459 /* ~Snap his neck when he leans in.~ */ GOTO 22
IF ~~ THEN REPLY #1460 /* ~Leave. Quickly.~ */ GOTO 15
END

