IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 18 // from: 6.4 9.0 9.1 9.4 16.4 17.4 40.4 40.5 41.6 50.6 53.6 61.4
SAY #1524 /* ~Soego takes a step back, then claps his hands together sharply three times. In response, a great iron bell starts tolling throughout the Mortuary.~ */
