IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 30 // from: 26.4 29.0
SAY #4860 /* ~Soego falls silent for a moment, studying you. His eyes gleam a bright red, and he gives a soft hiss. "I think you have outstayed your welcome." To your surprise, he takes a step back and claps his hands sharply three times. In response, a great iron bell starts tolling throughout the Mortuary.~ */
